broadwick.data.readers

Class BatchedMovementsFileReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • broadwick.data.readers.DataFileReader
      • broadwick.data.readers.BatchedMovementsFileReader

  • public class BatchedMovementsFileReader
extends DataFileReader
    Reader for the files describing the batched movements (i.e. those that do not specify an individual but rather the number of individuals moved)for the simulation. The movements are read and stored in internal databases for later use.
